  <brief_title>Historical Data Analysis of Complete Remission in Children With R/R Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia (ALL)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Retrospective Pooled Analysis of Complete Remission Among Pediatric Patients With Relapsed or Refractory B-cell Precursor Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia (ALL)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
